NIO provide the way to make IO operations via buffer 
and channel while tradition IO via streams(using native
methods). It is a faster way.
To learn:
http://blog.csdn.net/a953713428/article/details/64907250
http://blog.csdn.net/zcw4237256/article/details/78625193

2018/4/10:
In NIO, the class Files integrate comprehensive facilities 
in IO operations.

Two ways to handle IO affairs via NIO introduced in channelDemo
and mapChannelDemo, and other verbose operations using Files
ready to replace old IO operations in other files, are in 
this package.

